- Main structure:
  - `lib/my_app/` — domain logic, Ecto schemas, business rules.
  - `lib/my_app_web/` — web layer (controllers, channels, views).
  - `config/` — environment configs.
  - `test/` — ExUnit tests.
- Separate Contexts by domain.
- Avoid large, monolithic modules.
- Prefer clear naming: `MyApp.Accounts`, `MyApp.Billing`, etc.
